body:
The 19 and 34 versions are the same thing, but the 34 is each individual page and the 19 is the landscape of both pages.

The 54 version has both. If anything, the 54 version is the one with no point of existing.

So was there a point to the full 53 page version being uploaded, and then having two separate uploads of 19 pages and 34 pages, which is just the first one split up? That's literally the same thing uploaded twice, with the second one split into 2 uploads.
